http://www.chaos.org.uk/~jf/gnome-terminal-misc-fixed-fonts.xhtml

1. Get the fonts and save them at ~/.fonts
2. Create ~/.fonts/fonts.conf
3. fc-cache -fv
4. logout/login
5. gnome-terminal -> edit -> profile -> font -> Family: Fixed, Style: SemiCondensed, Size 10.

Inconsolata Font
cd ~/.fonts
wget http://kvz.io/assets/posts/Inconsolata.ttf
fc-cache -f -v

Application Fonts:

Emacs would no longer process setting the default font in ~/.emacs.  Instead,
create an alias '/bin/emacs -fn 6x13'


List fonts:
fc-list